channel.title: Got this new source for Delta and Need help:(
channel.description:
There is this welcome interface that is crooked on my screen when I login, and I was wondering, how I should take it off or center it for the client so it doesn't look bad.:( Im sorry if this is a newb question, I would like it if you could tell me where I should find this like client.java or is it client sided or server sided. I believe it's server sided but it's an interface so :/ Im just starting back up and wanted to have some fun with making this source and fixing everything and expanding it to be the best delta and maybe releasing (: [IMG]http://i1212.photobucket.com/albums/cc450/xray51/Iskapeclient.png[/img]
Sorry the sources name is SKclient and Source it's a package and the clients name is Iskape so The source maybe that aswell. Im just needing help sorry about the confusion.
